metadata.name: "Sea ​​Rise"
metadata.description:
I close my eyes and imagine...
Like the sunrise from the heart of the sea, peace is born from inside me. It flows in my blood and slowly surrounds me. My inner turmoil welcomes peace. I am passive here, passive as always, I submit myself to the waves of life and ask for peace from existence.

Implementation method: physical work plus digital animation
Style: Impressionism
Technique: oil on canvas
Size: 1080*1080

Date: February 2023
